    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In intellij just set Gradle JVM to Java version 17.</p>\n<p>&quot;File -&gt; Settings.. -&gt; Build, Execution, Deployment -&gt; Build Tools -&gt; Gradle&quot;\nthere select your project and set Gradle JVM to your java 17.0.1</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
