    "question_id" : 69696321,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Had the same problem, tried everything said above but no luck.</p>\n<p>Then saw this path <code>C:\\Program Files\\Common Files\\Oracle\\Java\\javapath</code> present in Systesm variable <code>path</code>. Deleting it solved the issue.</p>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: Don't forget to restart the terminal.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 8098318,
      "reputation" : 1836,
      "user_id" : 6102097,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/XAdbc.jpg?s=256",
