    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was running into this problem on GitHub Actions, building an APK with flutter. I setup Java with a specific version:</p>\n<pre><code>    - uses: actions/setup-java@v4\n      with:\n        distribution: 'temurin'\n        java-version: '17'\n    - run: java --version\n\n</code></pre>\n<p>GitHub Actions was using version 11.</p>\n"
