    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>One of the above answers might work in your case. In my case, it didn't - purely because of my own ignorance.</p>\n<p>I had hardcoded an older java home path a long time back in my local gradle properties file in <code>~/.gradle/gradle.properties</code></p>\n<p>Removing that stale entry fixed my issue.</p>\n"
